U.S. Navy SEAL Guide to Weather Secrets (U.S. Navy Seal Guide)

By Ralph Pezzullo, Don Mann


Epub -2012


Description

No matter where you are, you will have to deal with the weather—be it extreme heat or cold, snow or rain, wind or humidity, tornadoes or violent thunderstorms. How do you predict weather in the field? How do you prepare for it? Learn invaluable weather survival skills from expert Don Mann, who covers cloud interpretation for survival, danger warnings in the mountains, dealing with ultraviolet rays in high altitudes, weather forecasting with or without instruments, and much more
